          fiColumnHeader slJobList 
      WITH FRAME DEFAULT-FRAME IN WINDOW C-Win.
  ENABLE eInstructions fiEndDate fiThroughJob rsCompany bReview bPurge bExit 
         slJobList 
      WITH FRAME DEFAULT-FRAME IN WINDOW C-Win.
  {&OPEN-BROWSERS-IN-QUERY-DEFAULT-FRAME}
  VIEW C-Win.
END PROCEDURE.

